{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Cool thing Thursday: Dream of Pixels","content":"<p><em>Loading &#8230; random logic.</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5402\" style=\"width: 268px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/dream-of-pixels.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5402    \" title=\"Dream of Pixels\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/dream-of-pixels.png\" alt=\"Dream of Pixels\" width=\"258\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/dream-of-pixels.png 640w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/dream-of-pixels-200x300.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dream of Pixels</p></div>\n<p><em>Images &#8230; misplaced.</em></p>\n<p><em>Numbers &#8230; unidentified.</em></p>\n<p><em>Enter &#8230; erase.</em></p>\n<p>A few days ago I got my grubby little paws on <a href=\"http://dawnofplay.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Dawn of Play</a>&#8216;s next iOS gameÂ <em>Dream of Pixels</em>.</p>\n<p>Dram of Pixels is a simple game, one of those addicting little buggers you play whenever you&#8217;re waiting for a bus, something to compile or the person you are talking to takes 2.3 seconds too long to respond. Think tetris, but in reverse.</p>\n<p>Your goal is to clear falling lines of pixels by chopping out the familiar shapes from Tetris. There&#8217;s also a puzzle level and a nightmare and some things I haven&#8217;t unlocked yet. Topping it all off is a very nice soundtrack, shiny looks and a sexy female voice saying strange things about random logic.</p>\n<p>After losing the game lets you share an animated screenshot of the last thing you saw before waking up from the dream.</p>\n<p>You should pester <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zigah111\" target=\"_blank\">@zigah111</a> to give you access to the beta. It&#8217;s really fun.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 330px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://img.dawnofplay.com/dop/ss/as.php?s=17CB1E74-4D40-4F5F-8973-DE028DB5B207\"><img class=\" \" title=\"I'm not actually very good at this\" src=\"http://img.dawnofplay.com/dop/ss/screenshots/17CB1E74-4D40-4F5F-8973-DE028DB5B207.gif\" alt=\"I'm not actually very good at this\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">I&#8217;m not actually very good at this</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h6 class=\"zemanta-related-title\" style=\"font-size: 1em;\">Related articles</h6>\n<ul class=\"zemanta-article-ul zemanta-article-ul-image\" style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<li class=\"zemanta-article-ul-li-image zemanta-article-ul-li\" style=\"padding: 0; background: none; list-style: none; display: block; float: left; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; width: 84px; font-size: 11px; margin: 2px 10px 10px 2px;\"><a style=\"box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px #999; padding: 2px; display: block; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.awesome-robo.com/2012/08/the-beep-eijo.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0; display: block; width: 80px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://i.zemanta.com/106625121_80_80.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a style=\"display: block; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; line-height: 12pt; height: 80px; padding: 5px 2px 0 2px;\" href=\"http://www.awesome-robo.com/2012/08/the-beep-eijo.html\" target=\"_blank\">The Beep &#8211; Eijo</a></li>\n<li class=\"zemanta-article-ul-li-image zemanta-article-ul-li\" style=\"padding: 0; background: none; list-style: none; display: block; float: left; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; width: 84px; font-size: 11px; margin: 2px 10px 10px 2px;\"><a style=\"box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px #999; padding: 2px; display: block; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12651632/rmagick-pixel-color-value\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0; display: block; width: 80px; max-width: 100%;\" src=